{"word":"G3993 - πένης - pénēs - pen'-ace - Poor","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πένης</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pénēs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pen'-ace</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Poor</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஏழையான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"poor"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a primary &ldquo;peno&rdquo; (to <i>toil</i> for daily subsistence); <i>starving</i>, that is, <i>indigent</i>: - poor. Compare <a href=\"#/G4434 - πτωχός - ptōchós - pto-khos'/4434\">G4434</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}